INDUSTRY is mainly agriculture. There is some small holiday "letting" including a{CARAVAN SITE.}
LANGUAGE - in spite of newcomers from outside the area, there are still some local people who speak "Devonian", although these are dwindling, due to the cosmopolitan aspect of modern life. When heard however, it has a great fascination, and is being actively fostered by the {DEVON {DIALECT SOCIETY.}
MEDIA consists of newspapers, National and local; television and radio; magazines, local and National, including a lively {PARISH MAGAZINE, and FARMING publications.
